# zshrc_alias_for_hugo



## New aliases for the blog

Create the new post and pop open vim

```
hpost() {
  hugo new content content/posts/$1
  vim content/posts/$1
}

hnote() {
  hugo new content content/notes/$1
  vim content/notes/$1
}
```


